The paper focuses on automatic code comment generation, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The approach proposed in the paper involves mining comments from Stack Overflow, which is a programming language (cs.PL) Q&A site. The paper also mentions using heuristics to extract insightful comments, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the results of a user study, which could fall under the cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-category.
